snippet.title: Lil Wayne gives one of the most hilarious depositions ever (must see!)
snippet.description:
This video has been brought to you by http://bitshare.cm
More info here: http://bitshare.cm/news/watch-lil-wayne-give-one-of-the-funniest-depositions-ever-video/
Follow me on Twitter: http://twitter.com/DavidShares

This may go down as one of the funniest depositions in history. In a deposition that Lil Wayne gave related to a lawsuit he filed against Quincy Jones III over his 2009 documentary The Carter, Lil Wayne gives hilarious non-answers to the attorney. I can't believe the judge let it go down like this, even at one point where Lil Wayne clearly threatened the attorney! Video obtained and released by TMZ.

#LilWayne #Weezy #Funny
